						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Koṅgu, Kulōttuṅga Chōḻa, Year 13+1, Śaka 1085 = 1163 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>The king made a gift of land for offerings to the Vīrasangātap-perumbaḷḷi at Vijayamaṅgalam The land with a seed capacity of 3 <hi rend="italic">kalam</hi> was in some village (name lost) in Kuṟuppu-nāḍu. The king ordered his officials <hi rend="italic">(nan-tamar)</hi> not to disturb the gift.</p>						

